summary: This document appears to be a non-corporate signature page related to a Client Relationship Agreement with UBS. It outlines the terms and conditions for account management, including margin agreements and electronic delivery consent. The document emphasizes the responsibilities of the account holder and the implications of margin trading.
keyFacts: The document is a signature page for a Client Relationship Agreement with UBS.
It includes terms regarding margin trading and the responsibilities of the account holder.
The account holder has consented to receive documents electronically.
There is a mention of backup withholding and tax implications.
